# File sources and paths

## Images, videos, audios, inline images and code from files

All of this have the src of the image inside (src) exept the inline image that has it inside <-src->

The source can be a URL like `![A image](https://ThisIsAExampleImage.com/image.png)` or a file from the assets folder `![A image](assets/route/from/assets/image.png)`